entry.title: ytaras/scala_monad_slides
entry.summary:
scala_monad_slides

To run samples, install sbt first Then cd to project's directory and run sbt run command. It will download everything needed, compile and run sample program. Now you can start digging a code trying to understand what was shown in slides.
